rep_input: Patient HR+/HER2- progressed after CDK4/6; what key label-based caveats should I discuss?
model_output: For HR+/HER2- patients after progression on CDK4/6, subsequent therapy depends on prior endocrine treatments, performance status, and presence of visceral crisis. The label for each agent—whether endocrine, targeted, or chemotherapy—details specific indications and safety points, so please send the relevant SmPC or EMA summary by email for precise discussion.
